Name: Bomb
Description: An explosive device. As an action while holding the device, a creature may take an Action to make a ranged attack roll, throwing the device which detonates upon impact. When detonated, creatures within DISTANCE5-15DISTANCE feet must make a Dexterity saving throw (DC=DAMAGE10-20DAMAGE). On a failed save, a creature takes DAMAGE1-3DAMAGEd4 force damage, taking half damage and avoiding any other effects of the bomb on a successful one.
Requirements: Volatile
